description:
Gundam SEED fanfiction, the main plot is Gundam SEED anime content.

Interspersed with some extra plot in the middle.

No harem, no system, no golden fingers.

This is a story ordinary people struggling to survive through the SEED world.

The plot is classic and healing, have beautiful woman and handsome guys in this story.

The supporting characters not only have good IQ, good appearance, and good combat power, but also have layouts and plans throughout the story.
